ertscom or stay connected on twitter facebook or linkedin — end —   for more information stern dixon director of marketing office  cell  free initial consultation brian l kinsley mass tortproduct liability group leader  crumley roberts chat free initial consultation mycaseconnection™ portal call us   se habla español get help now contact a lawyer innorth or south carolina my name is  my phone number is  my email address is  i need help with aan  how can we help you brian l kinsley mass tortproducts liability practice group leader greensboro north carolina brian l kinsley is the mass tortproducts liability practice group leader at crumley roberts he earned his bachelor of science degree in criminal justice from northeastern university and went on to obtain his juris doctor cum laude from suffolk university law school he’s admitted to practice law in the district of columbia maryland massachusetts and north carolina including the united states district courts for the eastern middle and western districts of the state brian is married and has two children when he’s not at work he enjoys cooking and spending time outdoors education northeastern university bs suffolk university law school jd cum laude bar admissions and memberships north carolina state bar district of columbia bar maryland state bar massachusetts state bar admission to us district court – eastern middle  western districts of north carolina admission to us district court – massachusetts admission to us district court – southern district of illinois admission to us district court – new mexico american association for justice north carolina advocates for justice phi delta phi legal fraternity member of the national trial lawyers top  trial lawyers free initial consultation brian l roberts  imdb imdb more all titles tv episodes names companies keywords characters quotes bios plots movies tv  showtimes movies in theaters showtimes  tickets latest trailers coming soon release calendar top rated movies top rated