ph j roberts brian l roberts born june   is a jewish american businessman roberts is the chairman and chief executive officer ceo of comcast corporation an american company providing cable entertainment and communications products and services under his leadership comcast has grown into a global fortune  company uniquely positioned at the intersection of technology and media with two primary businesses comcast cable and nbcuniversal contents  early life and education  career  awards and philanthropy  maccabiah games  politics  personal life  references early life and educationedit roberts was born into a jewish family in philadelphia pennsylvania the son of ralph j roberts the founder of comcast corporation and suzanne fleisher a former actress and playwright roberts graduated from the germantown academy and earned a bachelor of science degree from the wharton school of the university of pennsylvania in  and immediately began working for comcast careeredit roberts is chairman and ceo of comcast corporation and personally controls   of the voting rights of the company he was named president of comcast corporation in  when the company had  million in annual revenue comcast corporation’s annual revenue has since grown to  billion roberts is chairman of the board of directors of the national cable  telecommunications association ncta and a former treasurer roberts served as chairman of ncta from  to  when the landmark deregulatory  telecommunications act became law in  roberts received us million in compensation and in  his net worth was us billion awards and philanthropyedit institutional investor magazine named roberts as its top votegetter for three years in a row – in the cable  satellite category of their americas best ceos annual survey and named comcast as one of americas most shareholderfriendly companies in  roberts was the recipient of the  humanitarian award from the simon wiesenthal center and was the  walter kaitz foundation honoree of the year for his commitment to diversity in the cable industry the police athletic league of philadelphia honored roberts with their  award for his commitment to youth programs and community partnerships in  roberts was awarded the usc shoah foundation institutes  ambassador for humanity award the aileen k and brian l roberts foundation was one of the largest contributors to the restoration of the alfred w fleisher memorial synagogue at eastern state penitentiary in philadelphia named in the honor of his maternal grandfather maccabiah gamesedit being an allamerican squash player and of jewish descent roberts participated in the maccabiah games in israel earning a gold medal with the us squash team in  and silver medals in    and  on october   roberts was honored by maccabi usa as a legend of the maccabiah politicsedit roberts was a founding cochair of philadelphia  the nonpartisan host committee for the  republican national convention the pennsylvania report named roberts to the  the pennsylvania report power  list of influential figures in pennsylvania politics calling him pennsylvania’s most powerful businessman and noted his influence with pennsylvania governor ed rendell in  roberts was named to the politicspa list of politically influential individuals since  roberts has donated more than  to democratic candidates and  to republican candidates in december  roberts wrote a letter to president barack obama endorsing the patient protection and affordable care act personal lifeedit roberts and his wife aileen kennedy roberts live in philadelphia with their three children aileen is the director of the barnes foundation roberts father is late comcast founder ralph j roberts and his mother is suzanne roberts in  roberts presented his mother along with his brother douglas and his father womens image network awards lifetime achievement award roberts owns a  ft sloop and a  ft sloop both designed by sparkman  stephens and named aileen after his wife which he sails whilst on holiday in his seasonal home on marthas vineyard referencesedit  a b brian roberts profile forbescom accessed august    a b comcast biography of mr brian l roberts retrieved  june    jewish daily forward top  jews  brian roberts retrieved december    jewish daily forward brian roberts jewish roots and outsized ambition drive comcasts rise in media forwardcom march    kellie patrick gates february   love suzanne fleisher roberts  ralph j roberts philadelphia inquirer   philadelphia inquirer a continual spotlight awaits a very private brian roberts att deal catapults comcasts chief to the industry forefront by benjamin y lowe december    comcast corporation website brian l roberts chairman and ceo comcast corporation comcastcom retrieved february    us cable industry launches take control its easy campaign to help parents manage their familys tv viewing april    comcast  mr brian l roberts compensation retrieved  june    a b brian l roberts press release retrieved april     michael elkin jewish exponent shoah salute personal meaning for comcast ceo jewishexponentcom may   accessed june    eastern state penitentiary funders for the synagogue restoration easternstateorg retrieved february    michael elkin shoah salute personal meaning for comcast ceo jewishexponentcom may   accessed june    maccabi usa  legends of maccabiah retrieved december    the pa report power  list pdf pennsylvania report capital growth inc january   archived from the original pdf on    power  politicspa the publius group  archived from the original on    hart kim  comcastnbc deal finds campaign cash converging with obamas principles the hill archived from the original on december   retrieved    roberts endorses ppaca politicocom accessed june    brian l roberts profile referenceforbusinesscom accessed june    aileen kennedy roberts profile businessweekcom retrieved july    philadelphia award   joseph neubauer and aileen roberts were honored for their work on the new barnes phillymagcom may    brian doug  ralph ro